#Maven Build
## Jenkins Pipeline - Maven Build

You will earn how to **compile, test and package a java project**


	pipeline {
		agent any
		tools {
			maven 'Maven-3.8.1'
			jdk 'JDK-17'
		}
		stages {
			stage('Checkout') {
				steps {
					gitl url: 'https://github.com/Pathnex/sample-java-app.git'
				}
			stage('Compile') {
				steps {
					sh 'mvn clean compile'
				}
			}
			stage('Test') {
				steps {
					sh 'mvn test'
				}
			}
			stage('Package') {
				steps {
					sh 'mvn package'
				}
			}
		}
	}